<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .blockquote {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your Comment Has Been Published!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= comment.user.name %>,</p>
            <p>Your comment has been successfully published and is now visible to others. Here's a quick preview of your comment:</p>
            <blockquote class="blockquote">
                "<%= comment.content %>"
            </blockquote>
            <p>Thank you for contributing to our community. Your insights and opinions are valuable.</p>
            <p>If you have any more thoughts to share or questions to ask, please feel free to participate in more discussions on our platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>The Codial Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
